The '''Brazi Power Station''' is a large [[thermal power plant]] located in [[Brazi]], having 9 generation groups, 5 of 50 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] each, 2 of 150 MW and 2 of 200 MW resulting a total [[electricity]] generation capacity of 950 MW.<ref>[https://www.scribd.com/doc/3283429/Energomontaj-IEA-Bucuresti Centrala Termoelectrica Brazi]</ref>

